What you need to know:

For the last 18 years it has kept the WRC Safari Rally dream alive, and last year served as a practical platform on which Kenya used to convince the International Motor Sports Federation (FIA) of the country's organisational acumenThe 2019 ARC Safari Rally FIA Candidate Event illustrated the immense potential and importance of Kenya as the most important geopolitical location in this part of the world from a sporting perspectiveThis is also a God-sent opportunity to put into practice what Kimathi's team has been preparing for the last one year